{"tid":1896391,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"袁國勇被問南韓與內地封關分別 笑答：政治既野我唔識呀下","createTime":"2020-02-25T06:01:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T06:45:27.000Z","uid":69091,"like":23,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"2c54f2e23ab290cf40b45bfe702326577a536fab","tid":1896391,"uid":69091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T06:01:03.000Z","msg":"【袁國勇：南韓形勢有些失控　林正財：要果斷堵截源頭】<br />\n<br />\n因應南韓新型肺炎疫情，政府對南韓發出紅色外遊警示。另外，由今日早上6時起不容許來自南韓、或14日內到過南韓的非香港居民，入境本港。<br />\n<br />\n港大微生物學系講座教授袁國勇及行政會議成員林正財在本台節目《千禧年代》表示，特區政府因應南韓疫情所採取的措施是較為果斷。<br />\n<br />\n袁國勇表示，本港除了一開始就口岸所實行的措施較遲外，其他措施都是跟隨科學精神。他說，目前南韓形勢有些失控，南韓當局找不到密切接觸者，認為是「無辦法不封」。林正財說，南韓當地確診個案上升得快，大邱市的疫情爆發有如當日的武漢，認為當地情況有些失控，要果斷堵截源頭。<br />\n<br />\n#香港電台<br />\n#南韓<br />\n#新型肺炎<br />\n#袁國勇<br />\n#林正財<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/715486135226112/posts/3245380538903313/?vh=e&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F715486135226112%2Fposts%2F3245380538903313%2F%3Fvh%3De%26d%3Dn&d=2snho0MtSZbn8sjHWbtmpX6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=7d46f88f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/715486135226112/posts/3245380538903313/?vh=e&amp;d=n</a><br />\n0:24開始睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6476ad39faa62cc9ba6d746bcad54502912d4952","tid":1896391,"uid":69091,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T06:01:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DDsS4gX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDDsS4gX.png&h=6053f16c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e53dd8f9cfe1d3b7d175a9efcb2ca737c92154a9","tid":1896391,"uid":263261,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T06:02:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.